		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://clockworktwist.com/?p=926</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[What a lovely Steampunk Style Party planning post!  I&#8217;d love to do something like this for Twist, next week. If you can&#8217;t already tell, I&#8217;m bursting with excitement!  My beautiful boy is going to be 3 years old in just seven more days.  Oh!  I&#8217;m ever so proud&#8230; If you haven&#8217;t already done it, go [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://thepartyconnection.wordpress.com/2013/02/20/steampunk-style-party/" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-928" alt="SP Party" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/sp-party.jpg" width="489" height="213" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/sp-party.jpg 489w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/sp-party-300x130.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 489px) 100vw, 489px" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align:left;">What a lovely <a href="http://thepartyconnection.wordpress.com/2013/02/20/steampunk-style-party/" target="_blank">Steampunk Style Party</a> planning post!  I&#8217;d love to do something like this for Twist, next week.</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">If you can&#8217;t already tell, I&#8217;m bursting with excitement!  My beautiful boy is going to be <strong>3 years old</strong> in just seven more days.  Oh!  I&#8217;m ever so proud&#8230;</p>
<p>If you haven&#8217;t already done it, go sign up for the Waking 2nd Edition paperback giveaway on Goodreads, <a href="http://www.goodreads.com/giveaway/show/62625-clockwork-twist---book-one-waking" target="_blank">right now</a>!  You&#8217;ve only got until the 30th, you know.</p>
<p>And don&#8217;t forget, the FREE Waking eBook release will be on Smashwords next Sunday!  If you already have a copy of the eBook, you can get the shiny new version for free as well, any time on or after the 17th.  Be the first one to get a look at the beginning of the new <a title="Book two : Trick" href="http://clockworktwist.com/book-two-trick/">Clockwork Twist, Book Two: Trick</a>!</p>
<p><a href="http://theculturalgutter.com/romance/whine-and-cheese.html" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignright" alt="" src="http://theculturalgutter.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/wine-settler-steampunk.jpg" width="270" height="208" /></a>Remember to raise a glass for Twist on the 17th.  Take your book/eReader out for cake and send in a photo, submit a piece of fan art complete with birthday hats, or whatever you want to do to celebrate our favorite, unassuming little clockmaker.   I&#8217;ll add everything I get to an extra special after-party post!</p>
<p>Together, let&#8217;s throw him a smashing birthday, shall we?</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
